If the 5080 didn't have as many issues and potential pitfalls as it does and was at MSRP, it still wouldn't be great value, but would be an even better upgrade for you.

Honestly I don't envy you, it's a crap situation and while AMD will probably have plenty of stock, there's a tonne of pent up demand so I don't think it will be any better once they launch.

